snippet.title: Twisted Trailer Final
snippet.description:
This is a trailer for the visual novel, Twisted. The third VN from Fablesoft Studios, this dark fairytale explores the frightening woods outside of a peaceful village, and the monster that resides there.

Game: https://fablesoft.itch.io/twisted
Webpage: https://fablesoft.itch.io/twisted
